        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[赢牛奶]#一喝牛奶就拉肚子是咋了#】医生介绍：这是乳糖不耐受的症状，小肠缺少乳糖酶，无法有效分解和吸收牛奶中的乳糖，就容易出现腹胀、腹痛、腹泻等症状。...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[赢牛奶]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/9c/2021_yingniunai_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%80%E5%96%9D%E7%89%9B%E5%A5%B6%E5%B0%B1%E6%8B%89%E8%82%9A%E5%AD%90%E6%98%AF%E5%92%8B%E4%BA%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%80%E5%96%9D%E7%89%9B%E5%A5%B6%E5%B0%B1%E6%8B%89%E8%82%9A%E5%AD%90%E6%98%AF%E5%92%8B%E4%BA%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#一喝牛奶就拉肚子是咋了#</span></a>】医生介绍：这是乳糖不耐受的症状，小肠缺少乳糖酶，无法有效分解和吸收牛奶中的乳糖，就容易出现腹胀、腹痛、腹泻等症状。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B9%B3%E7%B3%96%E4%B8%8D%E8%80%90%E5%8F%97%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B9%B3%E7%B3%96%E4%B8%8D%E8%80%90%E5%8F%97%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#乳糖不耐受可以改善吗#</span></a>？适当饮用，可逐步增加耐受，可以少量多次、避免空腹喝奶，还可以选择低乳糖、零乳糖牛奶或酸奶等👇🏻（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5005932048875529" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hn7ohfyze7j616c1kge8102.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Itx5UEuelx08cRhYp2bu01041200gEA10E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1192.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709010861&amp;ssig=udkR64i1lM&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/KJvZYO6Flx08cRhYEBM4010412009V4V0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x892.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709010861&amp;ssig=Z9NxCSW%2BaA&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/4vfxXhAllx08cRhXZjDi010412005p1Y0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x596.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709010861&amp;ssig=uk7mkrSqrs&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5005932048875529" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
